    @ConsumerType
 @FunctionalInterface
public interface HeptaConsumer<A,B,C,D,E,F,G>
    Defines a java.util.function.Consumer that takes seven input parameters. This consumer, like all consumers, doesn't return a result.

    This interface can be implemented with a lambda function.
